Title: Unshockable
Plot: When a band member of Rascal Flatts is electrocuted by his own guitar during a concert, the CSI team investigates if it was a case of foul play.
GuestStars: Jorja Fox, Will Patton, Rascal Flatts, Seth Gabel, Brent Briscoe, Alan Ruck, April Bowlby, Madison Mason, Archie Kao, Larry Sullivan, Jon Wellner, Dorian Christian Baucum, Carsten Norgaard, Lisa K. Wyatt
